query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('boot',
'command-line',
'dual-boot',
'installation',
'kubuntu',
'nautilus',
'partitioning',
'python',
'suspend',
'ubuntu-touch',
'uefi',
'virtualbox',
'xorg');
